    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a parts donor. The engine currently runs very roughly and exhibits several significant fluid leaks that will require immediate mechanical attention before it is roadworthy. Externally, the body shows signs of neglect with noticeable rust patches, fading paint, and several dents. The interior has seen heavy use, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please note that this car is sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
      "price": 3500.0,
